review:
I want to Just start out and say that Depop is an amazing platform to sell your items and other things to make some extra money. My problem is that when I refund the buyer for whatever reason and I emailed Depop for a seller fee and shipping label refund I never get a reply. I have gotten seller fee refunds in the past for this reason, however they take so long and sometimes you have to email them three times to even get in reply back. I am currently waiting on these people for a refund. It’s been a week now and still nothing. I’m missing $20 from my PayPal. I got emails from two different people saying hey refunded me...why wasn’t I refunded the first time?? Very very sketchy. Not cool. Also the app is glitchy at times. Other than that Depop is the best app to sell clothes on in my opinion. I just started 3 months ago and made hundreds so far.

Thanks,
@Evem70

